## 🤖 Automation Architecture

### Posting Schedule
| Time (EST) | Days |
|------------|------|
| 8:00 AM | Tue-Fri |
| 9:00 AM | Tue-Thu |
| 12:00 PM | Mon-Fri |
| 2:00 PM | Mon-Fri |
| 6:00 PM | Mon-Fri |

### Content Pipeline
```
GitHub Actions (cron) → Topic Selector + Diversity Guard
                             ↓
                Optional Search (Serper/Brave)
                             ↓
                    Groq API (generation)
                             ↓
                     Style Validation
                             ↓
                   Groq API (fact-check)
                             ↓
                   Twitter API → X Post → Archive
```

### Safeguards (All Active)
1. **Topic Alignment Validator** - Posts must mention approved topic
2. **Banned-Keyword Filter** - Blocks removed subjects
3. **Duplicate-Content Guard** - Scans ~250 prior posts
4. **Real-Time Search Trigger** - Version numbers auto-search
5. **Live-Context Cleanup** - Trailing domains stripped
6. **News Deduplication** - Normalized title comparison
7. **Regression Tests** - 6 tests, 100% passing

